: : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus looks at Nightlight, confused.

Rodimus Prime: Who said what?

OOC: Ok, so I just redid Azure&#39;s last Rodimus post.

: : Kup/Rodimus Prime : :

Kup is relieved that Nightlight is back, but remembers that he must still check the security of the Ark. He had left the Ark to battle the Preds when the Maximals made their move to get Nightlight back.

Kup opens a commlink with Rodimus Prime.

Kup: Roddy, I&#39;m going to go make sure that the Ark is secure. We dont want any random temporal disturbances.

Rodimus opens a return channel.

Rodimus Prime: Understood. Check back later.

Kup heads out of the Maximal base, transforming to vehical mode. He heads for the Ark.

: : Darkangel : :

Darkangel grows bored of sitting around the Tripredacus base. He opens a comm to DeathStar and Dreadplague.

Darkangel: Hey, you two. Since we arn&#39;t making a move right now, would you like to join me in the mess hall?

Darkangel heads for the mess hall, waiting for a reply.

: : DeathStar : :

DeathStar was looking over strategic reports on the Neo Beast Wars when he hears from Darkangel.

DeathStar: Sure, I could use a break. I&#39;ll be there in a few nano clicks.

DeathStar heads for the mess hall as well.

: : Wolfenstein/SharpClaws : :

Meanwhile at the Predacon base, Wolf has found SharpClaws.

Wolfenstein: I&#39;ve been looking for you. What is Hydras&#39; status?

SharpClaws: Not good. I could use your help.


